<div><head>《會稽記》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.2">少康封其少子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.3">號曰於越。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.4">越國之稱始於此。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.5">《史記‧越王句踐》、《世家正義》、《寶慶》、《會稽續志》一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.6">會稽山有禹井，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.7">去禹穴二十五步。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.8">謂禹穿鑿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.9">故因名之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-1a.10">《會稽》三賦周世則注。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.2">石簣其形似簣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.3">在宛委山上。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.4">《吳越春秋》：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.5">云在於九山東南，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.6">曰天柱山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.7">號曰宛委。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.8">其巖之巔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.9">承以文玉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.10">覆以磬石。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.11">其書金簡青玉為字，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.12">編以白銀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.13">皆篆其文。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.14">禹乃東巡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.15">登衡山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.16">殺白馬以祭之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.17">因夢見赤繡文衣男子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.18">自稱元夷倉水使者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.19">謂禹曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.20">欲得我簡書，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.21">知導水之方者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.22">齋於黃帝之岳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.23">禹乃齋三月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.24">登石簣山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.25">果得其文。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.26">乃知四瀆之脈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.27">百川之理，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.28">鑿龍門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.29">通伊闕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.30">遂周行天下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.31">到名山大澤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.32">召其神問之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.33">使伯益疏而記之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.34">名為《山海經》。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.35">《御覽》四十七。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.36">《寰宇記》九十六。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.37">防風氏身長三丈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.38">刑者不及，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.39">乃築高塘臨之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.40">故曰刑塘。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-2a.41">《輿地記‧勝十嘉秦》、《會稽志》二、《會稽》三賦注。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-3a.2">始寍。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-3a.3">順帝永建四年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-3a.4">分上虞南鄉立。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1697_CHANT_001-3a.5">《宋書‧州郡志》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
